works.description:
Sonko Jileng is principally engaged in the business of importing & retail sales of office furniture, stationery and equipment from Europe, The Middle East & U.S.A. 

In 1995 the company became the sole agent / distributor of all Canon products in the Gambia through its chain of stationery shops.

Retail Product Range:
• A4 & A3 copier paper
• Binding machines & covers
        Unibind Steel Crystal
• Calculators
• Colour printers
• Computer accessories
• Fax machines
• Filing Cabinets
• Photocopiers (small & high volume)
• Thermal laminating machines & film sheets
• Laser printer replacement cartridges
• Office Desks and Chairs
• Safes
• Wide range of stationery

.....and many other types of office and school supplies and equipment.

Sonko Jileng has a qualified team of technicians who are responsible for the installation and after sales service of all Canon photocopiers, fax machines, adding machines and calculators. To this end service contracts have been entered into with various companies guaranteeing them regular servicing of all their office equipments.

Staff strength now stands at over 25. In view of the importance of training as a basis of advancement, the company is committed to sponsoring training programs both locally and overseas, for its own benefit and for the benefit of the staff.
